We started campaigns but we don`t have any installs

Hi Anna, I'm sorry to hear that you're not seeing any installs from your campaigns. Could you please let me know which Mobile Measurement Partner (MMP) you are using for tracking? This will help me provide more specific guidance.

Thanks for letting me know, Anna. Here are the steps to ensure your Appsflyer tracking is correctly set up with NewsBreak:
1. Go to 'Integrated Partners' on Appsflyer and search for NewsBreak.
2. Select 'Attribution Link' under 'NewsBreak' and retrieve your tracking URLs.
3. Make sure you include the `af_prt` parameter on Appsflyer and share its value with your NewsBreak account manager to track attribution.
4. Enable the in-app event postbacks and use NewsBreak event_type for mapping. Ensure you include values & revenue on Appsflyer if you toggle on the Event value.
5. For iOS, deactivate the advanced policy to ensure NewsBreak can receive all conversion data.
For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [Introduction to App Install Events](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/26530008151309-Introduction-to-App-Install-Events).
If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!
